    <item>
      <title>特朗普对“无受害人”案件中 4.54 亿美元欺诈判决提出质疑</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-23/trump-challenges-454-million-fraud-verdict-in-victimless-case</link>
      <description><![CDATA[前总统唐纳德·特朗普请求曼哈顿上诉法院推翻针对他的 4.54 亿美元民事欺诈判决，称该案没有受害者，且裁决赋予纽约总检察长“无限权力”追捕政治对手。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-23/trump-challenges-454-million-fraud-verdict-in-victimless-case</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 23 Jul 2024 15:26:03 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>博茨瓦纳向公民承诺将持有新矿业公司 24% 的股份</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-23/botswana-touts-24-stake-in-new-mining-companies-for-citizens</link>
      <description><![CDATA[博茨瓦纳政府将鼓励新的矿业企业向公民提供购买高达 24％ 的国有股权的权利，而这些国有股权尚未被国家行使购买权。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-23/botswana-touts-24-stake-in-new-mining-companies-for-citizens</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 23 Jul 2024 15:23:34 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>拜登将于周三就退出 2024 年大选的决定发表讲话</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-23/biden-will-speak-wednesday-on-decision-to-drop-out-of-2024-race</link>
      <description><![CDATA[总统乔·拜登表示，他将于周三向全国发表讲话，说明结束连任竞选的决定。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-23/biden-will-speak-wednesday-on-decision-to-drop-out-of-2024-race</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 23 Jul 2024 15:18:42 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
