    <item>
      <title>特勤局局长因特朗普枪击事件辞职</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-23/secret-service-director-resigns-following-trump-shooting-furor</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国特勤局局长金伯利·奇特尔因对前总统唐纳德·特朗普在竞选集会上遭枪击的安全失误承担责任而辞职。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-23/secret-service-director-resigns-following-trump-shooting-furor</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 23 Jul 2024 14:55:11 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>英国工党考虑修改污染法规以放开住宅建设</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-23/labour-eyes-changing-uk-pollution-rules-to-unlock-housebuilding</link>
      <description><![CDATA[英国新工党政府将于周三与环保组织会面，寻求一种方法来解除目前受到反污染规则阻碍的规划项目，并兑现本届议会承诺的 150 万套新住房。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-23/labour-eyes-changing-uk-pollution-rules-to-unlock-housebuilding</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 23 Jul 2024 14:47:17 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>莫斯科为俄罗斯人在乌克兰作战提供创纪录的 22,000 美元</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-23/moscow-offers-record-22-000-for-russians-to-fight-in-ukraine</link>
      <description><![CDATA[莫斯科当局愿意向愿意参加俄罗斯乌克兰战争的新兵支付巨额奖金，这是为战场上阵亡和受伤的士兵寻找足够替代人员的压力越来越大的最新迹象。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-23/moscow-offers-record-22-000-for-russians-to-fight-in-ukraine</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 23 Jul 2024 14:42:19 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>布林肯支持哈里斯成为外交政策“领军人物”</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-23/blinken-vouches-for-harris-as-leading-voice-on-foreign-policy</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国国务卿安东尼·布林肯赞扬了副总统卡马拉·哈里斯在拜登政府外交政策中发挥的作用，以此表示对这位被认为在处理海外事务方面履历单薄的预定候选人的支持。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-23/blinken-vouches-for-harris-as-leading-voice-on-foreign-policy</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 23 Jul 2024 14:34:31 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>哈里斯在压力之下展开竞选活动，证明自己能够击败特朗普</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-23/harris-hits-trail-having-to-make-her-own-how-to-beat-trump-case</link>
      <description><![CDATA[副总统卡马拉·哈里斯将于周二在密尔沃基举行集会，正式启动她刚刚开始的总统竞选活动，试图回答民主党人心中最关心的问题：她打算如何击败唐纳德·特朗普？]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-23/harris-hits-trail-having-to-make-her-own-how-to-beat-trump-case</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 23 Jul 2024 09:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>1MDB 逃犯 Low 必须交出母亲的“完美无瑕”钻石</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-22/1mdb-fugitive-low-must-forfeit-mom-s-trio-of-flawless-diamonds</link>
      <description><![CDATA[刘特佐 (Low Taek Jho) 被控策划侵吞马来西亚 1MDB 基金，他被勒令没收三颗“完美无瑕”的钻石。这三颗钻石是他为母亲购买的，来自一家曾为碧昂斯 (Beyonce) 和阿黛尔 (Adele) 等名人设计珠宝的珠宝商。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-22/1mdb-fugitive-low-must-forfeit-mom-s-trio-of-flawless-diamonds</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 22 Jul 2024 23:11:43 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
